{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"15":"Jihad (Kitab Al-Jihad)"}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":2576,"arabicnumber":2576,"text":"حدثنا مسدد، حدثنا معتمر، عن عبيد الله، عن نافع، عن ابن عمر، أن نبي الله صلى الله عليه وسلم كان يضمر الخيل يسابق بها ‏.‏","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Muslim"}],"reference":{"book":15,"hadith":100}}]}